Document: ConcavePolygonShape2D
Path: godot/classes/class_concavepolygonshape2d.rst
Summary: The segments property defining line segments for a 2D concave polygon shape.

Property: segments (PackedVector2Array): The array of points forming line segments. The array length must be divisible by two, with each pair representing a segment's start and end points. Default: empty PackedVector2Array.

Method: set_segments(value: PackedVector2Array) → void
Method: get_segments() → PackedVector2Array

Note: The returned array is copied and modifications won't update the original property value. See PackedVector2Array documentation for details.